Proud to be a part of Unilever’s United We Stand 2023 where measurable change for our community is at the forefront. 
 
This is year 5 of @UnileverUSA United We Stand — a program to improve conditions in underserved and high risk LGTBQIA+ communities across the United States. The work will continue to support the life-changing mission of local grassroots organizations: @freedomoklahoma, @forumforequality, @tko_alabama, @Pflagswmo, @scblackPride and newly inducted @bhcfesouthdakota & #neaprogress. The initiative covers a spectrum of issues including anti-LGBT legislation, HIV decriminalization, conversion therapy, food insecurity and homelessness. 
 
Check out this year’s powerful film ‘Devoted to the Dream’ by @tourmaliiine as we celebrate queer joy and abundance. View the full film on her page. #UnitedWeStand #UnileverPartner
